      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think maxBuffer conforms to https://talks.golang.org/2014/names.slide#3 better\n\nNamely, it\u0027s still accurate, and is a maxBuffer of a size of an arbitrary unit, where the unit is documented in the comments.",
