      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-04T18:45:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done\n\nIf only I can do\nch :\u003d go fetch(...)\n\nWhich doesn\u0027t actually make any sense in Go, but made sense in my head.",
      "parentUuid": "31800a54_131d2e76",
      "range": {
