      "writtenOn": "2018-05-03T21:30:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Not necessary? Plus this comment leaves the Google Cloud Storage operation undefined. Storage is intentionally abstract - you have a storage, just say \"the Storage layer is responsible for performing low-level retries\" maybe?",
